                 <node depth="16" type="StaticText" id="" name="Customers find these curtains to be of good quality and appreciate their appearance, with one noting they look expensive. Moreover, the material receives positive feedback for being strong and smooth, while the color options and value for money are also well-received. Additionally, the curtains effectively block light, keep rooms cool, and work well for their intended purpose. However, opinions about light blocking are mixed, with some customers saying they block out all light while others disagree." value="Customers find these curtains to be of good quality and appreciate their appearance, with one noting they look expensive. Moreover, the material receives positive feedback for being strong and smooth, while the color options and value for money are also well-received. Additionally, the curtains effectively block light, keep rooms cool, and work well for their intended purpose. However, opinions about light blocking are mixed, with some customers saying they block out all light while others disagree." label="Customers find these curtains to be of good quality and appreciate their appearance, with one noting they look expensive. Moreover, the material receives positive feedback for being strong and smooth, while the color options and value for money are also well-received. Additionally, the curtains effectively block light, keep rooms cool, and work well for their intended purpose. However, opinions about light blocking are mixed, with some customers saying they block out all light while others disagree." enable="true" accessible="true" selected="false" index="303" visible="false" x="40" y="20586" width="756" height="442" bounds="[40,20586][796,21028]" nid="1602454216GXI4HRS0" childcount="0" left="40" top="20586" right="796" bottom="21028"></node> 
